---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "@/components/container.astro";
import Sectionhead from "@/components/sectionhead.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<Layout title="EU AI Act & MDR Compliance | AnichLabs OÜ">
  <Container>
    <Sectionhead>
      <Fragment slot="title">EU AI Act & MDR Compliance</Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">Risk classification, technical documentation, and compliance roadmaps for high-risk medical AI systems.</Fragment>
    </Sectionhead>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl mt-16">
      <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-100 rounded-2xl p-8">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-400 mb-3">The Problem</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">High-risk medical AI systems face strict EU obligations — and most teams don't know where to start</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">The EU AI Act classifies AI systems used in medical devices as high-risk by default. Combined with MDR requirements, this means conformity assessments, technical documentation, post-market surveillance, and human oversight mechanisms — all before your product can legally operate in Europe. Most health-tech teams have the technical skills but not the regulatory knowledge to navigate this.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl mt-10">
      <div class="rounded-2xl p-8" style="background-color: #EEF2FF; border: 1px solid #C7D2FE;">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3" style="color: #003399">The Solution</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">A clear, actionable compliance roadmap from risk classification to market readiness</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">AnichLabs OÜ maps your AI system against EU AI Act and MDR requirements, identifies your obligations, and delivers a written compliance roadmap with prioritised actions. We combine clinical judgment with regulatory expertise so your documentation reflects both technical reality and regulatory expectation.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8 text-center">What's Included</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:shield-check" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">EU AI Act Risk Classification</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Formal assessment of your AI system's risk level under the EU AI Act — minimal, limited, high-risk, or prohibited — with written justification.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:file-alt" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Technical Documentation Review</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Review and gap analysis of your existing technical documentation against EU AI Act Annex IV and MDR Annex II/III requirements.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:map" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Compliance Roadmap</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">A written, prioritised action plan mapping your gaps to specific regulatory requirements with timelines and resource estimates.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:eye" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Human Oversight Assessment</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Evaluation of your system's human oversight mechanisms against EU AI Act Article 14 requirements for high-risk systems.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:chart-bar" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Post-Market Surveillance Plan</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Design of a PMS plan meeting both EU AI Act and MDR requirements for continuous monitoring of your AI system in the field.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:file-check-alt" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Declaration of Conformity Support</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Guidance on preparing your EU Declaration of Conformity and CE marking process for medical AI systems.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-10 text-center">How It Works</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
        <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
          <div class="text-white rounded-full w-9 h-9 flex items-center justify-center font-bold shrink-0" style="background-color: #003399">1</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Discovery Call (free)</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-1">We discuss your AI system, its intended use, and current documentation status to confirm scope.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
          <div class="text-white rounded-full w-9 h-9 flex items-center justify-center font-bold shrink-0" style="background-color: #003399">2</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Risk Classification</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-1">We formally classify your system under the EU AI Act and MDR and provide a written classification report.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
          <div class="text-white rounded-full w-9 h-9 flex items-center justify-center font-bold shrink-0" style="background-color: #003399">3</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Gap Analysis</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-1">We review your technical documentation and processes against applicable requirements and identify all gaps.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
          <div class="text-white rounded-full w-9 h-9 flex items-center justify-center font-bold shrink-0" style="background-color: #003399">4</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Roadmap Delivery</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-1">You receive a written compliance roadmap with prioritised actions, timelines, and ongoing advisory options.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8 text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-5">
        <details class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-xl p-6 group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            Is my AI system automatically high-risk under the EU AI Act?
            <Icon name="uil:angle-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" />
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-4">If your AI system is a medical device or a safety component of a medical device, yes — it is classified as high-risk under the EU AI Act by default (Annex III). There are limited exceptions.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-xl p-6 group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            Do I need both EU AI Act and MDR compliance?
            <Icon name="uil:angle-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" />
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-4">If your product is a medical device with an AI component, you likely need to comply with both. They have overlapping but distinct requirements. We assess both together.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-xl p-6 group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            How long does compliance take?
            <Icon name="uil:angle-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" />
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-4">A gap analysis and roadmap takes 2–4 weeks. Achieving full compliance depends on your starting point — typically 3–12 months for a high-risk system.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-xl p-6 group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            Can you write the technical documentation for us?
            <Icon name="uil:angle-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" />
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-4">We can review, advise on, and guide the preparation of technical documentation. For full document authoring we work with specialist regulatory writers in our network.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl mt-20 mb-10 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">Ready to understand your EU AI Act obligations?</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-500 mt-3">Book a free 30-minute call and we'll confirm your risk classification and what compliance requires.</p>
      <a href="https://calendly.com/chris-anichlabs/30min" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
        class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors"
        style="background-color: #003399">
        <Icon name="uil:calendar-alt" class="w-5 h-5" />
        Book a Free Call
      </a>
    </div>

  </Container>
</Layout>
